      "content": "That \"enthusiastic behavior\" is making no sense in the telemetry. The sensors aren't picking up any crowds or vendor activity, just rhythmic, irregular stops and starts that look completely non-linear. It looks like the traffic is being diverted by some kind of pattern. Are you seeing something that isn't showing up on the standard sensor logs? Explain exactly what this \"gathering point\" looks like.",
